title: Obasquiat - Vermelho
text: I always suspected that we were animals, driven by our wishes, longings and desires, instincts and primitives. That inner fire that consumes us from one hour to the next, from night to day. Like animals thirsting for almost dreamlike sensations of some substance ... a strange atmosphere, surrounded by fog, as seen only in dreams - or when we drink too much or take some drugs.

title: Lijnenspel - Agressiestudie 1
text: Agressiestudie is a meditation on aggression through neutrally observing and materialising raw feelings and sounds. Raw pieces of steel wire and springs welded onto contact microphones transform gesture into sound. The input is buffered and granulised, to be able to inspect the motion over time.
